                  <desc> face plate of the Yale University Library, indicating it was a gift from
                    the estate of Harry M. Hyatt </desc>
                </item>
                <item xml:id="a1">
                  <locus target="#2r #43v #49r" facs="003 045 050"> f. 2r, 43v, 49r and
                    passim</locus>
                  <desc> mention owner, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መምሕር ገብረ ሥላሴ</foreign>, and scribe,
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሊቀረድ ተክለ ሃይማኖት</foreign>. 49r mentions the owner, his
                    father, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ እግዚአ</foreign>, and scribe </desc>
                </item>
              </list>
